1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:01:00,000
(Watch on www.kisskh.li Support Admin)

2
00:01:30,940 --> 00:01:33,960
[Episode 4]

3
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:47,455
Qing Long really hid the ledger with you.

4
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:50,760
You had a student help you
get rid of the bloody clothes,

5
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:53,079
making me think you left the city.

6
00:01:53,079 --> 00:01:56,944
Xia Liu Yi, how could you be so stupid?

7
00:01:57,959 --> 00:01:59,494
Who hit you?

8
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:02,497
Him.

9
00:02:04,799 --> 00:02:06,483
Which hand did he use?

10
00:02:07,599 --> 00:02:09,037
His left hand.

11
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:12,280
Let your boss avenge you.

12
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:15,319
I'm not your lackey.

13
00:02:15,319 --> 00:02:17,319
Give me a break, Xia Liu Yi.

14
00:02:17,319 --> 00:02:19,865
You can barely stand.
Stop pretending to be a big shot.

15
00:02:20,879 --> 00:02:22,857
Bring the ledger over.

16
00:02:39,159 --> 00:02:40,560
What?

17
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:42,500
Too scared to come get it?

18
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:46,919
You're full of dirty tricks.

19
00:02:46,919 --> 00:02:49,949
I'm not in the mood to play with you.

20
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:58,508
Don't move.

21
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:07,845
Boss, he's unarmed.

22
00:03:08,759 --> 00:03:11,560
I never carry a weapon.

23
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:13,319
Unlike your boss,

24
00:03:13,319 --> 00:03:15,929
who doesn't have any real weapon at all.

25
00:03:17,199 --> 00:03:19,260
It was his left hand, right?

26
00:03:22,759 --> 00:03:24,308
Liu Yi!

27
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:26,599
Xia Liu Yi.

28
00:03:26,599 --> 00:03:29,840
Watch your mouth
if you're in this line of work.

29
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:30,919
If you know what's good for you,

30
00:03:30,919 --> 00:03:32,360
say something nice.

31
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:34,319
If I'm in a good mood,

32
00:03:34,319 --> 00:03:36,784
maybe I'll leave your body intact.

33
00:03:39,231 --> 00:03:42,039
[Heroes of the Streets]
[Screenplay: He Chu San]

34
00:03:42,039 --> 00:03:43,040
What the hell is this?

35
00:03:43,040 --> 00:03:45,482
Wasn't this movie released last month?

36
00:03:48,319 --> 00:03:49,939
It's been switched.

37
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:53,319
Xu, I really didn't know about this.

38
00:03:53,319 --> 00:03:55,599
You little bastard, you dare mess with me?

39
00:03:55,599 --> 00:03:57,840
Where's the ledger?

40
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:59,719
Be honest.

41
00:03:59,719 --> 00:04:03,429
Xu, you killed Qing Long.

42
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:07,520
And you still didn't get
the most important ledger.

43
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:10,400
The Dragon Head Staff hasn't appeared either.

44
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:12,599
You can't become the new leader.

45
00:04:12,599 --> 00:04:14,800
Cut the crap.

46
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:16,680
I've captured you, the traitor.

47
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:17,940
That's a great achievement.

48
00:04:17,940 --> 00:04:20,839
And I've taken over all the gang's territory.

49
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:24,600
Those old bastards will have to
accept it whether they like it or not.

50
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:27,319
Qing Long treated you well.

51
00:04:27,319 --> 00:04:29,623
Why did you kill him?

52
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:33,776
Qing Long treated me well?

53
00:04:34,639 --> 00:04:36,639
I followed him for 20 years.

54
00:04:36,639 --> 00:04:39,480
I went through fire and raining blades for him.

55
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:41,399
And what did I get?

56
00:04:41,399 --> 00:04:45,839
In his eyes, there was only you,
a snot-nosed brat.

57
00:04:45,839 --> 00:04:49,003
It makes me sick.

58
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:54,360
What kind of useless deputy hall leader was I?

59
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:57,000
I was nothing but a dog at his feet.

60
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:59,160
When did he ever look at me seriously?

61
00:04:59,160 --> 00:05:01,839
Do you know what he told the elders?

62
00:05:01,839 --> 00:05:04,079
He said you are young,

63
00:05:04,079 --> 00:05:06,800
but both wise and brave,
worthy of great responsibility.

64
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:10,079
And that I, Xu Ying, am too scheming
to be fully trusted.

65
00:05:10,079 --> 00:05:11,923
Was he wrong?

66
00:05:12,959 --> 00:05:14,079
You bribed Cheng Shi Yong

67
00:05:14,079 --> 00:05:16,079
to switch my sister's medicine,

68
00:05:16,079 --> 00:05:17,240
and forced her to jump off a building.

69
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:18,879
You even stole my twin blades

70
00:05:18,879 --> 00:05:21,759
and stabbed my brother to death,
framing me for it.

71
00:05:21,759 --> 00:05:23,759
There were so many people in that villa.

72
00:05:23,759 --> 00:05:26,160
Do you really think you could
hide the truth from everyone?

73
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:28,079
So what?

74
00:05:28,079 --> 00:05:30,279
The brothers from Xiaoqi Hall
who were there that day,

75
00:05:30,279 --> 00:05:34,000
they weren't yours, they were all mine.

76
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:37,290
Who do you think they'll believe?

77
00:05:38,399 --> 00:05:40,240
Xu Ying.

78
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:42,639
Even in the underworld,
there are rules of honor.

79
00:05:42,639 --> 00:05:45,319
You killed so many innocent people.

80
00:05:45,319 --> 00:05:47,240
You won't die a good death.

81
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:49,316
Honor?

82
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:54,040
Everyone in the underworld said
Boss Long valued honor the most.

83
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:56,040
Did he die a good death?

84
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:58,360
Did he?

85
00:05:58,360 --> 00:06:00,876
Did he die a proper death?

86
00:06:02,108 --> 00:06:04,401
Fuck. Xia Liu Yi.

87
00:06:05,279 --> 00:06:06,920
Listen carefully.

88
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:09,279
Your corpse will be in pieces.

89
00:06:09,279 --> 00:06:14,560
Stubborn bastard, I'll crush you inch by inch.

90
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:17,037
Kill that student in front of him.

91
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:37,800
Xu Ying.

92
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:39,711
Who else are you going to kill?

93
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:17,862
Mr. Yuan of Xiaoqi Hall is here!

94
00:07:17,862 --> 00:07:19,630
Who dares to fire?

95
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:26,240
- Boss.
- Boss.

96
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:28,639
You deliberately had that student lure me here,

97
00:07:28,639 --> 00:07:30,622
and brought people to watch the show.

98
00:07:33,959 --> 00:07:35,560
A prestigious college student.

99
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:38,839
Award-winning screenwriter, top actor.

100
00:07:38,839 --> 00:07:42,759
Is my new lackey strong enough, Xu?

101
00:07:42,759 --> 00:07:44,040
Xia Liu Yi.

102
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,560
On the road to the underworld,

103
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:47,933
I'll have you serve as a body shield for me.

104
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:56,879
Xu Ying.

105
00:07:56,879 --> 00:07:58,199
Betrayed the gang.

106
00:07:58,199 --> 00:07:59,879
Conspired to harm the boss.

107
00:07:59,879 --> 00:08:02,759
By the rules, you deserve
three stabs and six wounds.

108
00:08:02,759 --> 00:08:05,491
What do you have to say for yourself now?

109
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:12,411
You ask what I have to say now?

110
00:08:13,280 --> 00:08:15,720
I lived and worked for Qing Long,

111
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:18,360
for all of you old fools,

112
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:21,160
sold my life for a lifetime.

113
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:24,891
In the end, all the benefits went to this kid.

114
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:31,040
Since you won't give it to me,
I'll take it myself.

115
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,918
What did I do wrong?

116
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:36,905
Three stabs and six wounds.

117
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:41,903
I... I don't accept it.

118
00:08:43,660 --> 00:08:45,459
I won't accept it.

119
00:08:53,399 --> 00:08:54,685
Boss.

120
00:08:59,559 --> 00:09:01,559
Xia Liu Yi.

121
00:09:01,559 --> 00:09:02,784
You...

122
00:09:06,919 --> 00:09:12,907
You'll never know how Qing Long died.

123
00:09:13,799 --> 00:09:15,426
What did you say?

124
00:09:33,759 --> 00:09:35,440
Explain yourself.

125
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:38,560
Explain clearly.

126
00:09:43,879 --> 00:09:45,944
Explain yourself!

127
00:09:45,944 --> 00:09:47,933
Explain it!

128
00:10:02,279 --> 00:10:04,519
Explain yourself!

129
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:09,087
Tell me clearly.

130
00:10:46,159 --> 00:10:48,067
I, Xia Liu Yi...

131
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:53,962
I will become the leader of Xiaoqi Hall.

132
00:10:59,159 --> 00:11:00,480
Boss.

133
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:16,420
Boss!

134
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:26,365
- Boss.
- Boss.

135
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:29,480
Boss.

136
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:30,639
Are you okay?

137
00:11:30,639 --> 00:11:32,879
- How are you?
- Are you okay?

138
00:11:34,279 --> 00:11:35,940
Let's go.

139
00:13:00,039 --> 00:13:03,415
This is a sin, truly a sin.

140
00:13:23,679 --> 00:13:25,468
Liu Yi.

141
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:29,435
Liu Yi, be careful!

142
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:32,799
Liu Yi.

143
00:13:32,799 --> 00:13:34,679
Liu Yi!

144
00:13:34,679 --> 00:13:38,159
My makeup's ruined.

145
00:13:38,159 --> 00:13:41,200
Dong Dong, you've been out for so long.

146
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:43,560
Did you miss me?

147
00:13:43,560 --> 00:13:45,840
Come on, tell me.

148
00:13:45,840 --> 00:13:47,519
Of course I did.

149
00:13:47,519 --> 00:13:49,240
I don't believe you. You're lying.

150
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:50,879
How could I lie to you?

151
00:13:50,879 --> 00:13:52,879
What's going on, Cui Dong Dong?

152
00:13:52,879 --> 00:13:54,600
This is my hospital room.

153
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:56,443
And you're flirting in here?

154
00:13:58,399 --> 00:14:01,600
The boss is really angry.

155
00:14:01,600 --> 00:14:03,919
Has the fierce tiger fallen on hard times?

156
00:14:03,919 --> 00:14:05,480
Didn't meet any beautiful women?

157
00:14:05,480 --> 00:14:08,600
And got outplayed by some student?

158
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:11,840
You must be frustrated.

159
00:14:11,840 --> 00:14:13,000
But then again,

160
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:15,480
that student's skin is so soft and smooth.

161
00:14:15,480 --> 00:14:17,960
Even old ladies drool over him.

162
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:20,639
Want to try a different flavor?

163
00:14:20,639 --> 00:14:22,927
Why not try the flowery road?

164
00:14:24,120 --> 00:14:26,379
You're really disgusting.

165
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:29,559
Spent a few days with a student,

166
00:14:29,559 --> 00:14:33,759
and you don't even recognize
a buddy of ten years.

167
00:14:33,759 --> 00:14:35,399
No wonder.

168
00:14:35,399 --> 00:14:37,995
This has been going on for so long,

169
00:14:38,879 --> 00:14:42,159
and now you come to me for help.

170
00:14:42,159 --> 00:14:44,360
If that student hadn't come to find me,

171
00:14:44,360 --> 00:14:46,994
I would've bought your coffin by now.

172
00:14:49,485 --> 00:14:52,039
I needed to disappear for long enough.

173
00:14:52,039 --> 00:14:53,799
Only then would Xu Ying fall for it.

174
00:14:53,799 --> 00:14:57,463
I hope you weren't hiding somewhere to cry.

175
00:15:01,600 --> 00:15:03,055
I'm sorry.

176
00:15:05,600 --> 00:15:07,932
I didn't protect them well.

177
00:15:16,639 --> 00:15:19,080
Since Xu Ying is already dead,

178
00:15:19,080 --> 00:15:21,120
there's no need to apologize.

179
00:15:24,480 --> 00:15:29,960
Qing Long and Xiao Man
have already been buried.

180
00:15:29,960 --> 00:15:31,973
Do you want to go see them?

181
00:15:44,399 --> 00:15:45,926
Help me set up a meeting with Mr. Yuan.

182
00:15:46,960 --> 00:15:48,901
I need to see him in person.

183
00:15:49,679 --> 00:15:51,921
He's supporting me to be the boss.

184
00:15:54,799 --> 00:15:56,968
I should greet him properly.

185
00:16:13,480 --> 00:16:15,720
- Xiao Ma.
- Boss.

186
00:16:15,720 --> 00:16:17,120
Boss.

187
00:16:17,120 --> 00:16:18,200
Boss!

188
00:16:18,200 --> 00:16:19,919
Boss, you're awake.

189
00:16:19,919 --> 00:16:21,560
What's your command?

190
00:16:23,000 --> 00:16:25,360
Help me check on something.

191
00:16:25,360 --> 00:16:28,519
Who did Xu Ying come into contact with before?

192
00:16:28,519 --> 00:16:30,480
Catch his trusted subordinates.

193
00:16:30,480 --> 00:16:32,519
Interrogate them one by one.

194
00:16:32,519 --> 00:16:33,759
Boss.

195
00:16:33,759 --> 00:16:36,039
Xu Ying's subordinates

196
00:16:36,039 --> 00:16:37,799
were all thrown into the sea last night.

197
00:16:37,799 --> 00:16:39,919
Not a single one is left.

198
00:16:39,919 --> 00:16:41,159
Who did this?

199
00:16:41,159 --> 00:16:42,279
The elders decided it.

200
00:16:42,279 --> 00:16:45,513
They said those guys were dangerous
and shouldn't be kept alive.

201
00:16:45,513 --> 00:16:49,000
Finally, something useful was done.

202
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:50,320
Those who used to be disobedient

203
00:16:50,320 --> 00:16:52,159
don't dare to say a word.

204
00:16:52,159 --> 00:16:54,600
It's really satisfying.

205
00:16:54,600 --> 00:16:57,986
I hope this is just to set an example.

206
00:16:59,559 --> 00:17:02,720
Boss, what do you mean?

207
00:17:02,720 --> 00:17:04,430
I don't understand.

208
00:17:07,400 --> 00:17:10,519
Go find Old K alone.

209
00:17:10,519 --> 00:17:11,880
Ask him to help me check

210
00:17:11,880 --> 00:17:14,839
who Xu Ying had contact with before.

211
00:17:14,839 --> 00:17:17,930
Don't let anyone know, including Dong Dong.

212
00:17:18,920 --> 00:17:20,364
Got it.

213
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:40,640
Make money, big money.

214
00:17:40,640 --> 00:17:44,005
Let's make big money together.

215
00:17:54,839 --> 00:17:57,680
Chu San, I've packed it for you.

216
00:17:57,680 --> 00:17:59,000
Here.

217
00:17:59,960 --> 00:18:02,640
- I'll get going, Fei.
- Okay, take care.

218
00:18:02,640 --> 00:18:05,481
- Got it.
- Take it slow, watch the road.

219
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:08,920
Chu San, your fever has gone down?

220
00:18:08,920 --> 00:18:11,485
Look at his little face, it's so skinny.

221
00:18:14,599 --> 00:18:15,981
Go up.

222
00:18:23,599 --> 00:18:25,182
Go up.

223
00:18:36,920 --> 00:18:38,640
Brothers.

224
00:18:38,640 --> 00:18:43,498
From now on, this nightclub
belongs to Xiaoqi Hall.

225
00:18:46,640 --> 00:18:48,319
Xiao Ma, come take a look.

226
00:18:48,319 --> 00:18:50,480
Did we hang it wrong?

227
00:18:50,480 --> 00:18:52,405
Can you fix it?

228
00:18:53,279 --> 00:18:55,531
Come. Stand over here.

229
00:19:09,519 --> 00:19:10,680
Chu San.

230
00:19:10,680 --> 00:19:11,720
Stop studying.

231
00:19:11,720 --> 00:19:13,440
Take a break.

232
00:19:15,000 --> 00:19:16,519
Chu San. Come on.

233
00:19:16,519 --> 00:19:19,357
Dad made you some soup for your brain.

234
00:19:20,880 --> 00:19:23,839
Chu San, have some soup.

235
00:19:23,839 --> 00:19:25,383
Thanks, Dad.

236
00:19:33,960 --> 00:19:36,640
Your frown could crush a fly.

237
00:19:36,640 --> 00:19:38,119
Your eyes are sinking in.

238
00:19:38,119 --> 00:19:40,085
How long have you not slept?

239
00:19:47,000 --> 00:19:48,160
Stop sleeping.

240
00:19:48,160 --> 00:19:50,279
Get up and keep working.

241
00:19:50,279 --> 00:19:51,532
Boss.

242
00:19:52,240 --> 00:19:53,839
What are you doing?

243
00:19:53,839 --> 00:19:55,975
Work time.

244
00:20:00,920 --> 00:20:02,640
Qi.

245
00:20:02,640 --> 00:20:05,559
That Xia Liu Yi is really arrogant.

246
00:20:05,559 --> 00:20:08,480
He not only seized our nightclub,

247
00:20:08,480 --> 00:20:10,508
but also beat me into this state.

248
00:20:17,480 --> 00:20:21,799
He even said that he would treat you like a dog

249
00:20:21,799 --> 00:20:23,558
and drive you out of Ganglong.

250
00:20:34,213 --> 00:20:35,599
Hello?

251
00:20:37,400 --> 00:20:39,550
Boss, it's Fei Qi.

252
00:20:45,903 --> 00:20:48,400
Hello, Qi.

253
00:20:48,400 --> 00:20:51,640
Xia Xiao Liu, what do you mean by this?

254
00:20:51,640 --> 00:20:53,920
Do we have some kind of misunderstanding?

255
00:20:53,920 --> 00:20:55,559
No, no, no.

256
00:20:55,559 --> 00:20:57,559
We don't have a misunderstanding.

257
00:20:57,559 --> 00:21:01,403
Today is just a meeting gift.

258
00:21:02,960 --> 00:21:04,965
My brother appeared to me in a dream.

259
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:08,480
He told me to cut down you, old dog.

260
00:21:08,480 --> 00:21:10,759
He wants me to send you to him.

261
00:21:10,759 --> 00:21:13,484
From now on, the stall belongs to us.

262
00:21:14,799 --> 00:21:16,493
Impressive.

263
00:21:24,119 --> 00:21:27,027
Qi, what do we do now?

264
00:21:29,938 --> 00:21:31,279
Trash.

265
00:21:31,279 --> 00:21:32,720
You're asking me?

266
00:21:32,720 --> 00:21:34,437
Who should I ask?

267
00:21:36,400 --> 00:21:38,041
Speak.

268
00:21:47,640 --> 00:21:50,480
That Dual Blades Xia from Xiaoqi Hall

269
00:21:50,480 --> 00:21:54,039
apparently seized another stall
from Hesheng Society yesterday.

270
00:21:54,039 --> 00:21:56,480
He was already wild when he was a top enforcer.

271
00:21:56,480 --> 00:21:59,799
Now that he's a boss, he's even more lawless.

272
00:21:59,799 --> 00:22:02,000
I heard he also opened a shady company.

273
00:22:02,000 --> 00:22:03,920
It's having its opening today.

274
00:22:03,920 --> 00:22:06,119
Yes.

275
00:22:06,119 --> 00:22:11,000
Let me tell you, this Fei Qi is part of
the Ho family from Hong Kong Island.

276
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:12,559
He's opposing Fei Qi.

277
00:22:12,559 --> 00:22:13,880
Isn't he afraid of being caught?

278
00:22:13,880 --> 00:22:16,759
Both of you, shut up.

279
00:22:16,759 --> 00:22:19,799
From now on, no talking
about the triads in this clinic.

280
00:22:19,799 --> 00:22:22,799
Your shop didn't have this stupid rule before.

281
00:22:22,799 --> 00:22:23,799
Now we do.

282
00:22:23,799 --> 00:22:25,880
What? Not following the rules?

283
00:22:25,880 --> 00:22:28,240
Then don't come here for cupping anymore.

284
00:22:28,240 --> 00:22:31,559
Dad, school starts today. I'm heading to class.

285
00:22:31,559 --> 00:22:32,759
Got your backpack on?

286
00:22:32,759 --> 00:22:33,839
Feeling better?

287
00:22:33,839 --> 00:22:35,200
Don't worry, Dad.

288
00:22:35,200 --> 00:22:36,799
Then don't carry too many books.

289
00:22:36,799 --> 00:22:38,359
- Got it.
- Be careful on the way.

290
00:22:38,359 --> 00:22:40,393
- Come back early.
- Got it.

291
00:22:40,393 --> 00:22:43,720
[Xiaoqi Trading]

292
00:22:43,720 --> 00:22:46,103
Mr. Yuan, do you like it?

293
00:22:53,480 --> 00:22:55,481
Good.

294
00:22:57,079 --> 00:22:59,039
Good.

295
00:22:59,039 --> 00:23:00,160
Great, Mr. Yuan.

296
00:23:00,160 --> 00:23:01,920
Wishing you wealth.

297
00:23:01,920 --> 00:23:03,599
Mr. Yuan.

298
00:23:03,599 --> 00:23:06,680
- Mr. Yuan.
- Mr. Yuan, wishing you wealth.

299
00:23:06,680 --> 00:23:08,680
Mr. Yuan, wishing you wealth.

300
00:23:08,680 --> 00:23:10,480
Wishing you wealth.

301
00:23:10,480 --> 00:23:11,799
Everyone will have wealth!

302
00:23:11,799 --> 00:23:14,160
Mr. Yuan, wishing you wealth.

303
00:23:14,160 --> 00:23:15,160
Come, come.

304
00:23:15,160 --> 00:23:16,983
Everyone gets some.

305
00:23:18,200 --> 00:23:20,045
And me, Mr. Yuan?

306
00:23:29,200 --> 00:23:30,799
Thanks a lot, Mr. Yuan.

307
00:23:30,799 --> 00:23:32,458
Live a long life.

308
00:23:40,920 --> 00:23:42,505
Abandon.

309
00:24:14,359 --> 00:24:15,480
What are you looking at?

310
00:24:15,480 --> 00:24:16,720
Spotted a babe?

311
00:24:16,720 --> 00:24:18,393
Where?

312
00:24:23,480 --> 00:24:24,960
Me!

313
00:24:24,960 --> 00:24:26,599
Come on, you too.

314
00:24:26,599 --> 00:24:29,319
Mr. Yuan, wishing you wealth and good health.

315
00:24:29,319 --> 00:24:31,021
Good.

316
00:24:31,021 --> 00:24:32,000
[Xiaoqi Trading]

317
00:24:32,000 --> 00:24:34,010
Everyone gets some.

318
00:25:08,479 --> 00:25:09,480
Chu San, don't laugh.

319
00:25:09,480 --> 00:25:11,039
Hold his hands down.

320
00:25:11,039 --> 00:25:13,060
Don't move.

321
00:25:15,359 --> 00:25:17,005
You look...

322
00:25:17,880 --> 00:25:20,512
much more impressive than when you were here.

323
00:25:23,640 --> 00:25:26,034
You should be very satisfied
with your life now.

324
00:25:29,400 --> 00:25:33,799
A ruthless gangster like you saved me twice.

325
00:25:33,799 --> 00:25:35,479
I've repaid you twice.

326
00:25:36,240 --> 00:25:38,446
We should be even now.

327
00:25:48,240 --> 00:25:49,921
We...

328
00:25:51,319 --> 00:25:53,868
Shouldn't have any more entanglements.

329
00:26:15,480 --> 00:26:18,278
Boss, Fei Qi has gone into hiding with his wife
and kids in Hung Hom for two weeks.

330
00:26:18,278 --> 00:26:20,319
We haven't caught him.

331
00:26:20,319 --> 00:26:23,480
How did you manage that? Can't you think?

332
00:26:23,480 --> 00:26:25,680
I'll go catch him now.

333
00:26:25,680 --> 00:26:27,640
Hung Hom is Fei Qi's territory.

334
00:26:27,640 --> 00:26:29,680
His men are everywhere on the streets.

335
00:26:29,680 --> 00:26:31,240
You're asking for death.

336
00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:33,480
Xiao Ma isn't very bright.

337
00:26:33,480 --> 00:26:34,960
Are you the same?

338
00:26:34,960 --> 00:26:37,000
Kowloon is already ours.

339
00:26:37,000 --> 00:26:39,680
Only that coward Fei Qi is left.

340
00:26:39,680 --> 00:26:42,759
We can deal with him later.

341
00:26:42,759 --> 00:26:44,640
He brought it on himself
by challenging my brother.

342
00:26:44,640 --> 00:26:47,759
Boss, don't chase a cornered enemy.

343
00:26:47,759 --> 00:26:50,056
Do you understand?

344
00:26:56,240 --> 00:26:57,880
In the past two months,

345
00:26:57,880 --> 00:26:59,559
we've taken so much territory from Fei Qi,

346
00:26:59,559 --> 00:27:01,279
and opened so many shops.

347
00:27:01,279 --> 00:27:03,400
Even if you want to be a workaholic,

348
00:27:03,400 --> 00:27:05,119
you still have to let them rest.

349
00:27:05,119 --> 00:27:07,960
The company is running now,

350
00:27:07,960 --> 00:27:09,640
so give them some time off.

351
00:27:09,640 --> 00:27:11,519
If the brothers have the chance to earn,

352
00:27:11,519 --> 00:27:14,465
they need time to spend too, right?

353
00:27:15,400 --> 00:27:16,937
Rest?

354
00:27:21,960 --> 00:27:23,541
Want a break?

355
00:27:25,240 --> 00:27:26,719
No, Boss.

356
00:27:26,719 --> 00:27:27,720
Time off?

357
00:27:27,720 --> 00:27:31,400
For the boss, I'll go through anything.

358
00:27:31,400 --> 00:27:32,839
You got hit just yesterday.

359
00:27:32,839 --> 00:27:34,768
It doesn't hurt anymore, huh?

360
00:27:35,599 --> 00:27:37,960
It's fine, just a small injury.

361
00:27:37,960 --> 00:27:39,472
All right.

362
00:27:40,720 --> 00:27:44,480
Tell your guys that bonuses will be doubled,

363
00:27:44,480 --> 00:27:45,799
and they get two days off.

364
00:27:45,799 --> 00:27:47,731
In a few days...

365
00:27:49,920 --> 00:27:51,359
Are you kidding me?

366
00:27:51,359 --> 00:27:52,960
Who am I making money for?

367
00:27:52,960 --> 00:27:55,468
All of them are heartless.

368
00:27:58,200 --> 00:27:59,920
Not only do we give time off,

369
00:27:59,920 --> 00:28:01,359
we're hiring more people too.

370
00:28:01,359 --> 00:28:08,559
Especially those who are smart,
can read, can handle accounts,

371
00:28:08,559 --> 00:28:10,960
and can manage people and shops.

372
00:28:10,960 --> 00:28:13,964
I think your apprentice is pretty good.

373
00:28:27,599 --> 00:28:30,000
- Got any discs?
- Fuck!

374
00:28:30,000 --> 00:28:32,200
You came here just to watch videos?

375
00:28:32,200 --> 00:28:34,720
Do you have any ambition?

376
00:28:34,720 --> 00:28:36,119
Come, someone!

377
00:28:36,119 --> 00:28:37,680
Coming!

378
00:28:37,680 --> 00:28:39,119
Hurry!

379
00:28:39,119 --> 00:28:40,530
Come over quickly.

380
00:28:42,039 --> 00:28:43,519
Move faster, be quick.

381
00:28:43,519 --> 00:28:44,760
Greet Liu Yi.

382
00:28:44,760 --> 00:28:45,799
Hurry. Come.

383
00:28:45,799 --> 00:28:47,079
Liu Yi.

384
00:28:47,079 --> 00:28:48,240
Boss Xia.

385
00:28:48,240 --> 00:28:50,319
Pick whoever you like.

386
00:28:50,319 --> 00:28:53,170
Today, I'll cover everything.

387
00:28:53,170 --> 00:28:54,559
Damn.

388
00:28:54,559 --> 00:28:56,000
How did she sneak in?

389
00:28:56,000 --> 00:28:57,680
- She collects garbage.
- Are you an adult?

390
00:28:57,680 --> 00:29:00,239
- I'm an adult.
- Didn't I tell you to send her back?

391
00:29:00,239 --> 00:29:01,240
I'm not leaving.

392
00:29:01,240 --> 00:29:02,599
I-I-I'm not going back to Cao Dong.

393
00:29:02,599 --> 00:29:04,240
I I want to be a prostitute.

394
00:29:04,240 --> 00:29:06,279
I... I...

395
00:29:06,279 --> 00:29:08,079
A stutter.

396
00:29:08,079 --> 00:29:10,240
What are you doing,
bringing someone like this here?

397
00:29:10,240 --> 00:29:11,720
Send her back to the boat.

398
00:29:11,720 --> 00:29:13,370
Wait.

399
00:29:14,160 --> 00:29:15,319
Boss.

400
00:29:15,319 --> 00:29:17,039
I'm very smart.

401
00:29:17,039 --> 00:29:18,839
I'm not going back to Cao Dong.

402
00:29:18,839 --> 00:29:20,000
From Cao Dong?

403
00:29:20,000 --> 00:29:21,359
Don't mess with me.

404
00:29:21,359 --> 00:29:23,279
No minors allowed here.

405
00:29:23,279 --> 00:29:24,599
If she doesn't work, am I supposed
to let her freeload off us?

406
00:29:24,599 --> 00:29:25,920
I'm not running a charity.

407
00:29:25,920 --> 00:29:28,079
I want her.

408
00:29:28,079 --> 00:29:30,000
You said it yourself.

409
00:29:30,000 --> 00:29:31,909
I choose, you pay.

410
00:29:32,799 --> 00:29:35,043
Xia Liu Yi, I really...

411
00:29:36,599 --> 00:29:38,000
Boss.

412
00:29:38,000 --> 00:29:39,994
Get lost.

413
00:29:41,000 --> 00:29:43,633
Time for me to be happy.

414
00:29:47,480 --> 00:29:48,799
- Move.
- Go, out of the room.

415
00:29:48,799 --> 00:29:50,480
Hurry. Don't look.

416
00:29:50,480 --> 00:29:53,480
Don't look. Move it.

417
00:29:53,480 --> 00:29:55,602
Don't look. Hurry up.

418
00:30:04,079 --> 00:30:05,524
Stop.

419
00:30:08,559 --> 00:30:10,480
Stay here for the night.

420
00:30:10,480 --> 00:30:12,480
Sleep.

421
00:30:12,480 --> 00:30:14,814
Tomorrow, get the money from Cui Dong Dong.

422
00:30:39,680 --> 00:30:42,008
[Children's Day]

423
00:31:25,079 --> 00:31:26,960
Hao.

424
00:31:26,960 --> 00:31:29,480
Do I look good in these clothes?

425
00:31:31,920 --> 00:31:32,960
You're his sister.

426
00:31:32,960 --> 00:31:35,079
He thinks you look good in anything.

427
00:31:35,079 --> 00:31:37,038
That's true.

428
00:32:34,839 --> 00:32:36,680
Damn kid.

429
00:32:36,680 --> 00:32:38,501
He Chu San.

430
00:32:49,240 --> 00:32:50,655
Sir.

431
00:32:52,200 --> 00:32:54,200
Sir, out for a morning workout?

432
00:32:54,200 --> 00:32:55,548
Chu San.

433
00:33:19,480 --> 00:33:21,720
Y-You guys...

434
00:33:21,720 --> 00:33:23,525
He Chu San.

435
00:33:58,759 --> 00:34:01,559
That day on the bus,

436
00:34:01,559 --> 00:34:03,466
did you peek at me?

437
00:34:08,000 --> 00:34:10,999
I hadn't even said which day,
but you shook your head so fast.

438
00:34:14,880 --> 00:34:17,044
Fei's beef offal.

439
00:34:19,519 --> 00:34:20,520
Why aren't you speaking?

440
00:34:20,520 --> 00:34:22,291
I'll beat you to death.

441
00:34:25,639 --> 00:34:27,280
What are you doing here?

442
00:34:27,280 --> 00:34:29,442
I came to get my blade.

443
00:34:30,880 --> 00:34:33,840
The knife? How do you know it's here?

444
00:34:33,840 --> 00:34:34,840
Stay here, don't move.

445
00:34:34,840 --> 00:34:36,355
I'll go get it for you.

446
00:34:37,119 --> 00:34:39,660
Let's go. Lead the way.

447
00:34:39,660 --> 00:34:41,360
Let's use the back door.

448
00:34:41,360 --> 00:34:43,984
I never use the back door.

449
00:34:55,180 --> 00:35:02,639
The past feels like a fleeting dream,
and it's hard to recognize my feelings...

450
00:35:10,079 --> 00:35:13,474
Sirs, are you here for a consultation?

451
00:35:15,280 --> 00:35:16,902
Here to present a banner.

452
00:35:16,902 --> 00:35:19,365
[Medicine Cures All]
[To: Mr. He, From: Xia Liu Yi]

453
00:35:38,280 --> 00:35:40,127
Mr. Xia.

454
00:35:46,239 --> 00:35:47,892
Chu San!

455
00:35:53,000 --> 00:35:55,079
You... He...

456
00:35:55,079 --> 00:35:56,500
Dr. He.

457
00:35:58,119 --> 00:35:59,920
A miracle doctor.

458
00:35:59,920 --> 00:36:02,119
Thank you for your care before.

459
00:36:02,119 --> 00:36:04,360
I've come specifically

460
00:36:04,360 --> 00:36:06,480
to present a banner

461
00:36:06,480 --> 00:36:09,015
and a red envelope.

462
00:36:10,760 --> 00:36:12,239
You need to show respect.

463
00:36:12,239 --> 00:36:14,079
Do you know what respect means?

464
00:36:14,079 --> 00:36:15,119
Sorry.

465
00:36:15,119 --> 00:36:17,053
Say it again.

466
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:21,559
Mr. Xia, you're too polite.

467
00:36:21,559 --> 00:36:23,840
You're being too polite.

468
00:36:23,840 --> 00:36:26,239
Forget the banner and the red envelope.

469
00:36:26,239 --> 00:36:27,628
Dr. He.

470
00:36:30,639 --> 00:36:33,000
Just call me "Xia Liu Yi".

471
00:36:34,320 --> 00:36:36,679
He Chu San.

472
00:36:36,679 --> 00:36:38,760
Take me to get the knife.

473
00:36:38,760 --> 00:36:39,880
Knife?

474
00:36:39,880 --> 00:36:41,760
Dad, don't worry.

475
00:36:41,760 --> 00:36:43,843
You eat first. I'll grab the knife.

476
00:36:50,119 --> 00:36:51,573
Come with me.

477
00:36:55,519 --> 00:36:57,960
Dr. He!

478
00:36:57,960 --> 00:37:00,320
Where do we hang this?

479
00:37:00,320 --> 00:37:03,180
Hang it...

480
00:37:38,920 --> 00:37:40,280
Where did you put it?

481
00:37:40,280 --> 00:37:41,880
In the pickled vegetables jar.

482
00:37:41,880 --> 00:37:43,493
What the heck?

483
00:37:46,760 --> 00:37:48,880
Do you know you've committed a mortal sin?

484
00:37:48,880 --> 00:37:51,239
This was given to me by my brother.

485
00:37:51,239 --> 00:37:54,679
Bow! Hear that?

486
00:37:54,679 --> 00:37:55,920
Come back and bow before me.

487
00:37:55,920 --> 00:37:57,913
I'm not your underling.

488
00:38:00,000 --> 00:38:02,239
Not my underling...

489
00:38:02,239 --> 00:38:04,503
My ears are getting calluses from hearing this.

490
00:38:06,119 --> 00:38:07,939
Take me to your room.

491
00:38:10,280 --> 00:38:11,960
What do you want?

492
00:38:11,960 --> 00:38:13,519
Of course, there's something I want.

493
00:38:13,519 --> 00:38:15,553
Why do you have so many questions?

494
00:38:28,400 --> 00:38:31,917
This room is even more run-down
than I remembered.

495
00:38:36,639 --> 00:38:39,159
Join Xiaoqi Hall.

496
00:38:39,159 --> 00:38:43,320
I'll buy you a sea-view apartment in Hung Hom.

497
00:38:43,320 --> 00:38:45,599
You can even bring your dad over.

498
00:38:45,599 --> 00:38:47,639
You can live comfortably.

499
00:38:47,639 --> 00:38:49,011
How about it?

500
00:38:51,320 --> 00:38:52,981
No thanks.

501
00:38:54,599 --> 00:38:56,800
You're pretending to be high and mighty.

502
00:38:56,800 --> 00:38:59,989
One day, you'll regret it.

503
00:39:04,079 --> 00:39:07,937
Your bed is still so comfortable.

504
00:39:19,800 --> 00:39:21,746
How's your injury?

505
00:39:39,280 --> 00:39:40,903
Xia Liu Yi.

506
00:41:33,880 --> 00:41:35,865
Did you sleep well?

507
00:41:40,400 --> 00:41:42,067
It was okay.

508
00:41:49,119 --> 00:41:51,533
How's your injury now?

509
00:41:52,519 --> 00:41:53,840
My injury?

510
00:41:53,840 --> 00:41:56,360
It's healed already.

511
00:41:56,360 --> 00:42:01,313
With my build, I just need a week.

512
00:42:01,313 --> 00:42:06,177
I healed completely in just a week.

513
00:42:07,840 --> 00:42:09,079
You...

514
00:42:10,953 --> 00:42:14,719
[Medicine Cures All]
[To: Mr. He, From: Xia Liu Yi]

515
00:42:14,719 --> 00:42:17,239
Mr. Xia, the acupuncture points
I apply pressure on

516
00:42:17,239 --> 00:42:18,280
might hurt a little.

517
00:42:18,280 --> 00:42:20,280
Endure it.

518
00:42:20,280 --> 00:42:21,719
It'll hurt?

519
00:42:21,719 --> 00:42:24,403
I never cry out in pain.

520
00:42:27,480 --> 00:42:29,119
Boss.

521
00:42:29,119 --> 00:42:30,400
What are you doing?

522
00:42:30,400 --> 00:42:31,925
You...

523
00:42:35,199 --> 00:42:37,039
Get out.

524
00:42:37,039 --> 00:42:39,529
- Boss.
- Out.

525
00:42:47,039 --> 00:42:48,342
Dad.

526
00:42:49,119 --> 00:42:50,928
Take it easy.

527
00:42:53,039 --> 00:42:54,920
Mr. Xia, your tendons are torn.

528
00:42:54,920 --> 00:42:56,599
Here, the blood and energy are stagnant,

529
00:42:56,599 --> 00:42:57,639
and the tissues are sticking together.

530
00:42:57,639 --> 00:42:59,320
If we don't loosen them,

531
00:42:59,320 --> 00:43:00,679
they'll hurt even without touching them.

532
00:43:00,679 --> 00:43:01,679
Chu San.

533
00:43:01,679 --> 00:43:02,719
Hold his hand down.

534
00:43:02,719 --> 00:43:04,443
Don't let him move.

535
00:43:25,280 --> 00:43:26,992
Careful, you...

536
00:43:32,679 --> 00:43:33,840
All right.

537
00:43:33,840 --> 00:43:35,494
Go get the car.

538
00:43:45,519 --> 00:43:50,390
This place is even scarier than
Xiaoqi Hall's torture room.

539
00:43:53,920 --> 00:43:55,960
What are you looking at?

540
00:43:55,960 --> 00:43:57,599
It's just one injured arm.

541
00:43:57,599 --> 00:43:59,840
I don't need you to compensate me.

542
00:43:59,840 --> 00:44:02,470
If it weren't for you saving me twice,

543
00:44:03,679 --> 00:44:05,394
you wouldn't be hurt like this.

544
00:44:06,639 --> 00:44:08,920
You helped me out.

545
00:44:08,920 --> 00:44:10,894
I can't just watch you die.

546
00:44:11,840 --> 00:44:14,159
But you got hurt.

547
00:44:14,159 --> 00:44:16,519
You can't wield dual blades.

548
00:44:16,519 --> 00:44:19,052
H-How do you be the boss?

549
00:44:22,559 --> 00:44:26,079
Being a boss isn't just about wielding blades.

550
00:44:26,079 --> 00:44:27,639
You also need to use your brain.

551
00:44:27,639 --> 00:44:29,549
Do you understand?

552
00:44:38,840 --> 00:44:40,188
Bye.

553
00:44:41,639 --> 00:44:43,031
Xia Liu Yi.

554
00:44:47,480 --> 00:44:49,350
Would you be willing

555
00:44:50,159 --> 00:44:52,444
to come to my graduation ceremony?

556
00:45:00,460 --> 00:45:04,459
[Medicine Cures All]
[To: Mr. He, From: Xia Liu Yi]

557
00:45:15,239 --> 00:45:18,480
Dad, I'll take it down for you.

558
00:45:18,480 --> 00:45:20,418
Nah, just leave it there.

559
00:45:21,840 --> 00:45:23,639
Dad.

560
00:45:23,639 --> 00:45:25,320
Aren't you the one
who hates the triads the most?

561
00:45:25,320 --> 00:45:33,996
Chu San, if I forbid you from speaking to
Liu Yi and his buddies, can you do it?

562
00:45:35,320 --> 00:45:37,840
Dad, I...

563
00:45:37,840 --> 00:45:38,920
All right.

564
00:45:38,920 --> 00:45:41,902
I know you can't do it.

565
00:45:43,239 --> 00:45:48,719
Actually, Liu Yi isn't bad at heart.

566
00:45:48,719 --> 00:45:50,951
It's a shame he went down the wrong path.

567
00:45:52,000 --> 00:45:56,079
Some matters are doomed fates.

568
00:45:56,079 --> 00:45:58,401
They're all destined.

569
00:45:59,960 --> 00:46:03,934
What I can do as a father is bear it with you.

570
00:46:05,679 --> 00:46:07,400
But I really worry.

571
00:46:07,400 --> 00:46:10,870
You are influenced by the company you keep.

572
00:46:12,239 --> 00:46:14,039
Dad.

573
00:46:14,039 --> 00:46:18,584
Perhaps it isn't Liu Yi influencing me,

574
00:46:18,584 --> 00:46:20,550
but me influencing him instead.

575
00:46:28,239 --> 00:46:30,017
You've grown up.

576
00:47:14,920 --> 00:47:17,840
Scar Li, leave the shop to me.

577
00:47:17,840 --> 00:47:19,480
The goods from me, Sha Jia Jun,

578
00:47:19,480 --> 00:47:21,960
are sourced from that person.

579
00:47:21,960 --> 00:47:24,280
Not at all inferior to Xiaoqi Hall's.

580
00:47:24,280 --> 00:47:29,636
I'll take all your goods of this quality.

581
00:47:36,079 --> 00:47:38,512
Don't move! Police!

582
00:48:00,159 --> 00:48:01,480
Sha Jia Jun.

583
00:48:01,480 --> 00:48:03,000
Big boss of the Sha gang.

584
00:48:03,000 --> 00:48:04,480
Smuggling and drug trafficking.

585
00:48:04,480 --> 00:48:06,320
Organizing mafia activities.

586
00:48:06,320 --> 00:48:08,079
You are now officially under arrest.

587
00:48:08,079 --> 00:48:09,360
You have the right to remain silent.

588
00:48:09,360 --> 00:48:12,280
Anything you say can be used
as evidence in court.

589
00:48:12,280 --> 00:48:15,599
A mere inspector dares to mess with me?

590
00:48:15,599 --> 00:48:17,159
Do you even know who's behind me?

591
00:48:17,159 --> 00:48:19,999
You chief inspectors should be serving me tea.

592
00:48:19,999 --> 00:48:22,119
Is that so?

593
00:48:22,119 --> 00:48:23,599
Then you might as well say it straight out.

594
00:48:23,599 --> 00:48:25,966
I'll send him in to keep you company.

595
00:48:35,079 --> 00:48:37,519
Mr. He, your son is truly
a remarkable young man.

596
00:48:37,519 --> 00:48:40,760
I heard he even got
an acceptance letter from Citibank.

597
00:48:40,760 --> 00:48:42,559
It's all because of his own hard work.

598
00:48:42,559 --> 00:48:44,599
He has loved reading since he was young.

599
00:48:44,599 --> 00:48:45,960
He doesn't even watch television.

600
00:48:45,960 --> 00:48:47,159
Yeah.

601
00:48:47,159 --> 00:48:49,800
So, do you have any secrets
in raising children?

602
00:48:49,800 --> 00:48:50,960
I wouldn't say I have any secrets.

603
00:48:50,960 --> 00:48:53,410
But I do have some experience.

604
00:48:56,039 --> 00:48:57,800
Chu San, what's the matter?

605
00:48:57,800 --> 00:48:59,239
Is someone coming over?

606
00:48:59,239 --> 00:49:01,239
No, no.

607
00:49:01,239 --> 00:49:02,880
Chu San, come over.

608
00:49:02,880 --> 00:49:04,800
Let me take a photo of you.

609
00:49:04,800 --> 00:49:06,360
Yes, let's go.

610
00:49:06,360 --> 00:49:07,719
Go up there.

611
00:49:07,719 --> 00:49:09,760
Come on, Fei.

612
00:49:09,760 --> 00:49:11,719
- Come on.
- Give it to me.

613
00:49:11,719 --> 00:49:12,760
Be careful.

614
00:49:12,760 --> 00:49:13,800
Watch your step.

615
00:49:13,800 --> 00:49:15,760
- Are you okay?
- I'm fine.

616
00:49:15,760 --> 00:49:17,679
Don't break Mr. Hua's camera.

617
00:49:17,679 --> 00:49:19,403
Got it.

618
00:49:22,239 --> 00:49:23,463
Come on.

619
00:49:25,679 --> 00:49:26,679
Smile a little.

620
00:49:26,679 --> 00:49:30,079
Today is your big day.

621
00:49:30,079 --> 00:49:31,535
Smile.

622
00:49:34,159 --> 00:49:36,480
Hey, how about I do it?

623
00:49:36,480 --> 00:49:37,679
- Okay, okay.
- You go over.

624
00:49:37,679 --> 00:49:39,350
Okay.

625
00:49:40,880 --> 00:49:42,633
Dad, wait a minute.

626
00:49:52,159 --> 00:49:53,320
I'm here.

627
00:49:53,320 --> 00:49:55,480
Everyone is here, and you're still at home.

628
00:49:55,480 --> 00:49:56,760
Sorry, I mistook you for someone else.

629
00:49:56,760 --> 00:49:58,280
It's okay.

630
00:49:58,280 --> 00:49:59,599
Come over quickly.

631
00:49:59,599 --> 00:50:01,538
Did you hear me?

632
00:50:03,559 --> 00:50:05,119
Chu San, what are you doing?

633
00:50:05,119 --> 00:50:06,519
Come over quickly.

634
00:50:06,519 --> 00:50:07,920
Yes, come quickly.

635
00:50:07,920 --> 00:50:09,880
Come on.

636
00:50:09,880 --> 00:50:12,239
Stand there, and you'll be fine.

637
00:50:12,239 --> 00:50:14,119
Straighten your clothes.

638
00:50:14,119 --> 00:50:15,280
So handsome.

639
00:50:15,280 --> 00:50:17,679
Okay, come on, look over here.

640
00:50:17,679 --> 00:50:19,199
Okay, smile.

641
00:50:19,199 --> 00:50:22,480
You look great. Look here.

642
00:50:22,480 --> 00:50:25,740
Three, two, one, smile.

643
00:50:25,740 --> 00:50:27,133
Smile.
